      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUDICIARY (4) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 383m behind Mister Easy (23.25) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money prior to that. Has ability and looks hard to stop. LORD SHYLOCK (2) last start finished 4th in a Grade 5 on April 5 over 383m at this track behind BING BING SECRET beaten 9 lengths (23.16). Looks well placed here and among the chances. LAWN KEEPER (1) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 43 from 93 starts. Finished in the minors latest when third (31.99) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Solid record at the distance winning seven races. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings nine times from 14 attempts. Winning chance. IMPRESS TILLY (8) has claims again if she runs up to the latest effort.",
